  m_text: "Welcome to portal of a cosmic merchant! In this journey, you will travel
    between the primitive Stone Age and the futuristic Tech Era, negotiating deals
    with powerful local leaders.\n\nYour path to riches lies in 'Temporal Arbitrage':
    leveraging the logic of different eras to buy low and sell high. While your wealth
    grows passively by 1 Gold every second, the true challenge is outmaneuvering
    the market. \n\nYour ultimate objective? Amass a fortune that surpasses the world's
    wealthiest individual and cement your legacy as the master of time and coin."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 86f0d920f8e8d864181dc9d2d1446c4b, type: 2}
